se.aqba.framework.elpollo

Class ElPollo

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.aqba.framework.elpollo.ElPollo

  • public final class ElPollo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that contains various classes and methods to add method overrides and replace resources.


    To find out how to load your override classes, look at ElPolloModuleLoader and ElPolloModule.
    For adding overrides, have a look at ElPollo.Packages.addListener(Listener, String...), ElPollo.MemberOverride and ElPollo.Overrides.
    Adding resource replacements can be done using ElPollo.Resources.addListener(Listener, String...) and the various addReplacement methods.
